Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Fear of Russia returns
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xb01
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 25 Sep 1983
President Reagan under pressure as fear of Russia returns following the shooting-down of the Korean airliner. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less